tika.dc.description: Just what you need to bring everyone to the dinner table! Our Favorite Comfort Foods Recipes cookbook has over 60 of the creamy, cheesy, sweet & savory recipes we all love and crave. Start the day with a smile and scrumptious golden french toast and then serve up a family-pleasing dinner of mom's sloppy joes or homestyle chicken pot pie. Chase away the sniffles with prairie bacon-corn chowder and spoil everyone a little with double-chocolate brownies...they're almost as good as a hug from Grandma!
